Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来袭名第8代篠田麻里子
